Usage: merge_vtm [-help] -config <string> [-format <string>]
                 [-merged_file <string>] [-rundir <string>]

-help                     # Prints out the command usage
-config <string>          # <config_file_name> (string, required)
-format <string>          # <output format of the map> (string, optional)
-merged_file <string>     # <outout file name> (string, optional)
-rundir <string>          # <run directory> (string, optional)